### Variables Production
@baseUrl = https://backend-taxi-e2lz.onrender.com/api
@contentType = application/json
@telephone = +21698765440

### 1. Créer un nouveau client
POST {{baseUrl}}/clients
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "nom": "Test Prod",
    "prenom": "Client1",
    "email": "test.prod1@example.com",
    "telephone": "{{telephone}}"
}

### 2. Demander OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/send-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "telephone": "{{telephone}}"
}

### 3. Voir le dernier code OTP (développement uniquement)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/debug/last-otp/{{telephone}}

### 4. Vérifier OTP
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/verify-otp
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "telephone": "{{telephone}}",
    "code": "REMPLACER_PAR_CODE_RECU"
} 